title: Week 5 preview & Cardinals vs. 49ers recap
itunes:title: Week 5 preview & Cardinals vs. 49ers recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, and Marc Sessler – go game-by-game recapping each week 5 matchup. Plus, the heroes recap the Thursday night NFC West showdown between the Arizona Cardinals and the San Francisco 49ers
